name: GOST vs. SONNY (SKRILLEX TEE)
description:
EXCLUSIVE first of its kind collaboration between Sonny Moore and GOST Brand Clothing.  This is the first shirt ever created for Sonny's DJ alter-ego SKRILLEX!  This GOST vs. SONNY shirt features original artwork by GOST Brand artist Arlo Eisenberg.  It is available in limited quantities and you can ONLY get it here!

Plastisol ink printed on a black fitted (American Apparel style) T-shirt.
